rComments: Communicates concepts well in class and handwriting easy to understand. Midterm had one tricky question (may be indicative that I didn't study enough), and the exam was fair. Assignments are fair indication as to what to expect. Distinguished ability to motivate attendance through east euro allure.

Hectic class, lots of material, though not lots of difficult material. She's a good teacher, exams were fair, and it doesn't hurt that she's cute too, in a distinctly eastern-european-lady kinda way. Accent isn't too bad.
